testcase.name: VCAP::Services::Redis::Node Node.start_provisioned_services should check whether provisioned service is running or not
VCAP::Services::Redis::Node Node.start_provisioned_services should not start a new instance if the service is already started when start all provisioned services
VCAP::Services::Redis::Node Node.start_provisioned_services should start a new instance if the service is not started when start all provisioned services
